## Satellite & Aerial Imagery

| Tool | Description | Free | Origin |
|------|-------------|------|--------|
| [Google Earth Pro](https://www.google.com/earth/about/versions/) | Historical satellite imagery | ✅ | 🇺🇸 USA |
| [Sentinel Hub](https://www.sentinel-hub.com) | ESA satellite imagery (Sentinel, Landsat) | 🔶 Freemium | 🇸🇮 Slovenia |
| [Copernicus Browser](https://browser.dataspace.copernicus.eu) | Free ESA satellite data browser | ✅ | 🇪🇺 EU |
| [Bing Maps](https://www.bing.com/maps) | Aerial imagery, sometimes more recent than Google | ✅ | 🇺🇸 USA |
| [Maxar](https://www.maxar.com) | High-resolution commercial satellite imagery | ❌ Paid | 🇺🇸 USA |
| [Planet Labs](https://www.planet.com) | Daily satellite imagery of the entire Earth | ❌ Paid | 🇺🇸 USA |
| [NASA Worldview](https://worldview.earthdata.nasa.gov) | Near real-time satellite imagery (NASA) | ✅ | 🇺🇸 USA |

